{"ts":"2026-06-25T23:20:40.283Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Analyzing Dependencies and Imports**\n\nI'm making great headway, I believe. The dependency version is clear, using `\"motion\": \"^12.40.0\"`, and the import path is \"motion/react\". Now, I'm setting my sights on drafting `components/sections/InteractiveExperienceSection.tsx`. I am going to see how that file is structured and where we are importing those files.\n\n\n**Refining Subcomponents' Designs**\n\nOkay, I'm focusing intently on the interactive tools. I'm designing `InteractiveExperienceSection.tsx`, ensuring each subcomponent, like \"Talk to Agent,\" is self-contained. I'm aiming for a fully interactive, bug-free TypeScript file. I've re-examined the initial structure, noticing the import of `SectionHeading`. I'm going to start by including the mockup.\n\n\n**Designing Interactive Components**\n\nI'm now detailing the \"Talk to Agent\" feature. My focus is on simulating a realistic chat experience, including a greeting and preset prompts like \"Optimize Cloud Inventory.\" The system will handle user input, setting a loading state, and then, after 800ms, streaming a detailed, technical response. I'm building out a robust response map for preset prompts, plus a fallback for custom messages. The goal is a premium feel for how the responses appear. I'm also planning the design for a \"Blueprint Generator\" section.\n\n\n**Evaluating AI Readiness**\n\nI've shifted focus to an AI readiness assessment. I'm visualizing interactive sliders for Data Integration, Compliance & Guardrails, and Agent Architecture, each on a scale of 1 to 5. I'm building a dynamic readiness score that updates in real time based on slider positions, visualizing this with a progress wheel that shifts from red to green. The goal is to provide personalized, concise recommendations based on the score, including a smooth scroll option to the blueprint generator.\n\n\n**Calculating ROI Values**\n\nI'm now detailing an ROI calculator with three sliders: automated workgroup size, manual task hours per employee per week, and hourly blended labor rate. My calculations include annual hours reclaimed, annual dollars saved, implementation investment, net profit, and ROI ratio. The display will format the savings, hours, and ROI values elegantly. I've also outlined the structure for a marketplace section showcasing premium tools, each with metadata and a \"Activate to Sandbox\" option.\n\n\n**Visualizing Studio Flow**\n\nI'm now implementing the Foundry Studio's visual canvas, focusing on the core nodes: ERP Data Source, Cognitive Orchestrator, Compliance Filter, and Automated Output. I'm prioritizing animating pulses flowing between these nodes to show a clear visual workflow, using either CSS animations or timed states to manage this. I'm also planning the interactive configuration panels for each node, which will have a sleek, user-friendly design.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-25T23:20:40.288Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"j27fuw1c","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/sections/InteractiveExperienceSection.tsx","old_text":"import SectionHeading from \"@/components/SectionHeading\";\n\nexport default function InteractiveExperienceSection() {\n  const items = ['Talk to Agent', 'Blueprint Generator', 'AI Readiness', 'ROI Calculator', 'Marketplace', 'Foundry Studio'];\n  return (\n    <section className=\"w-full bg-[#030303] px-6 lg:px-16 lg:py-20 py-12\">\n      <SectionHeading\n        title={\n          <h2 className=\"text-[24px] sm:text-[30px] leading-none font-medium text-center uppercase text-white\">\n            INTERACTIVE <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">EXPERIENCE</span>\n          </h2>\n        }\n        titleClassName=\"text-center\"\n        dividerWidthClassName=\"w-[260px]\"\n      />\n      <div className=\"mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n        {items.map(c => (\n          <div key={c} className=\"group relative rounded-[20px] p-[1px] bg-white/5 hover:bg-gradient-to-r hover:from-[#E4000F] hover:to-[#009DFF] transition-all cursor-pointer\">\n            <div className=\"h-full rounded-[19px] bg-[#000102] p-8 flex flex-col justify-center min-h-[180px] text-center\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white/90 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\">{c}</h3>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  )\n}","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport { useState, useEffect, useCallback, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport SectionHeading from \"@/components/SectionHeading\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\n\ninterface Message {\n  sender: \"user\" | \"agent\";\n  text: string;\n  isLog?: boolean;\n}\n\nexport default function InteractiveExperienceSection() {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<number>(0);\n\n  const tools = [\n    {\n      id: \"talk\",\n      name: \"Talk to Agent\",\n      tagline: \"Interact with GFF's multi-agent orchestrator.\",\n      link: \"/build/talk\",\n      color: \"#009DFF\",\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"blueprint\",\n      name: \"Blueprint Generator\",\n      tagline: \"Map custom enterprise agent structures.\",\n      link: \"/build/blueprint\",\n      color: \"#E98828\",\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"assessment\",\n      name: \"AI Readiness\",\n      tagline: \"Measure compliance and capability gaps.\",\n      link: \"/build/assessment\",\n      color: \"#9D00FF\",\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"roi\",\n      name: \"ROI Calculator\",\n      tagline: \"Model cost reduction and business savings.\",\n      link: \"/build/roi\",\n      color: \"#E4000F\",\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"marketplace\",\n      name: \"Marketplace\",\n      tagline: \"Browse validated agent pipelines & plug-ins.\",\n      link: \"/platforms/marketplace\",\n      color: \"#0186E4\",\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"foundry\",\n      name: \"Foundry Studio\",\n      tagline: \"Visually orchestrate secure neural workflows.\",\n      link: \"/platforms/foundry\",\n      color: \"#00FF9D\",\n    },\n  ];\n\n  // Tool 1: Talk to Agent State & Responses\n  const [chatMessages, setChatMessages] = useState<Message[]>([\n    {\n      sender: \"agent\",\n      text: \"System initialized. Cognitive Core online. GFF multi-agent supervisor ready to execute high-impact objectives. Select a scenario below or input custom prompt.\",\n    },\n  ]);\n  const [chatLoading, setChatLoading] = useState<boolean>(false);\n  const [chatInput, setChatInput] = useState<string>(\"\");\n  const chatBottomRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);\n\n  const chatPresetResponses: Record<string, { summary: string; steps: string[] }> = {\n    \"optimize cloud spend\": {\n      summary: \"Identified $45,200 annual recurring idle cost reduction across AWS and hybrid-cloud Kubernetes clusters with zero application SLA degradation.\",\n      steps: [\n        \"Core Supervisor parsed cloud telemetry pipeline.\",\n        \"Resource Auditor identified 14 non-production instances without reservation profiles.\",\n        \"SLA Evaluator cross-referenced application throughput SLAs (OK to downgrade during off-peak).\",\n        \"Action Planner scheduled automated down-scaling crons.\",\n      ],\n    },\n    \"audit compliance & security\": {\n      summary: \"Automated real-time compliance scan across active S3 buckets and IAM policies. Isolated 3 legacy policy drift vectors.\",\n      steps: [\n        \"Core Supervisor triggered policy validation loop.\",\n        \"Security Guardrail scanned 42 public-facing cloud profiles.\",\n        \"PII Shield verified auto-redaction functions in active datastores.\",\n        \"Audit Engine generated SOC2 compliance logs for review.\",\n      ],\n    },\n    \"verify supply chain route\": {\n      summary: \"Re-routed 12 critical shipments around active port bottlenecks. Integrated port delays API with SAP logistics pipelines.\",\n      steps: [\n        \"Core Supervisor identified logistics latency spikes.\",\n        \"API Integration agent queried port congestion registries.\",\n        \"Route Optimizer calculated 3 alternative terrestrial corridors.\",\n        \"ERP Adapter queued automated shipping schedule updates in SAP.\",\n      ],\n    },\n  };\n\n  const handleSendChat = useCallback(\n    (text: string) => {\n      if (!text.trim() || chatLoading) return;\n      const userText = text;\n      setChatMessages((prev) => [...prev, { sender: \"user\", text: userText }]);\n      setChatInput(\"\");\n      setChatLoading(true);\n\n      setTimeout(() => {\n        const cleanKey = userText.toLowerCase().trim();\n        const preset = chatPresetResponses[cleanKey];\n\n        if (preset) {\n          // Stream steps and then summary\n          setChatMessages((prev) => [\n            ...prev,\n            { sender: \"agent\", text: \"Analyzing task. Triggering specialized agent cohort...\", isLog: true },\n          ]);\n\n          let delay = 600;\n          preset.steps.forEach((step, idx) => {\n            setTimeout(() => {\n              setChatMessages((prev) => [...prev, { sender: \"agent\", text: `[Step ${idx + 1}] ${step}`, isLog: true }]);\n            }, delay);\n            delay += 500;\n          });\n\n          setTimeout(() => {\n            setChatMessages((prev) => [\n              ...prev,\n              {\n                sender: \"agent\",\n                text: `Execution complete. Executive summary: ${preset.summary}`,\n              },\n            ]);\n            setChatLoading(false);\n          }, delay + 400);\n        } else {\n          // Generic response\n          setChatMessages((prev) => [\n            ...prev,\n            { sender: \"agent\", text: `Resolving intent: \"${userText}\"...`, isLog: true },\n          ]);\n          setTimeout(() => {\n            setChatMessages((prev) => [\n              ...prev,\n              {\n                sender: \"agent\",\n                text: `Successfully initialized specialized execution loop for custom command. Cognitive Core has logged this pipeline request. Connect GFF agents to your private VPC database in the full console to activate end-to-end sandbox operations.`,\n              },\n            ]);\n            setChatLoading(false);\n          }, 1200);\n        }\n      }, 600);\n    },\n    [chatLoading]\n  );\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    chatBottomRef.current?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n  }, [chatMessages, chatLoading]);\n\n  // Tool 2: Blueprint Generator State\n  const [bpObjective, setBpObjective] = useState(\"optimize\");\n  const [bpInt, setBpInt] = useState(\"api\");\n  const [bpSec, setBpSec] = useState(\"vpc\");\n  const [bpGenerated, setBpGenerated] = useState(false);\n  const [bpGenerating, setBpGenerating] = useState(false);\n\n  const handleGenerateBp = () => {\n    setBpGenerating(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setBpGenerated(true);\n      setBpGenerating(false);\n    }, 900);\n  };\n\n  const scrollSmoothToBlueprintSection = () => {\n    const el = document.getElementById(\"blueprint\");\n    if (el) {\n      el.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Tool 3: AI Readiness State\n  const [rdData, setRdData] = useState(3);\n  const [rdCompliance, setRdCompliance] = useState(2);\n  const [rdAgent, setRdAgent] = useState(2);\n\n  const rdScore = Math.round(((rdData + rdCompliance + rdAgent) / 15) * 100);\n  const getRdTier = (score: number) => {\n    if (score >= 85) return { name: \"Optimized Enterprise\", desc: \"Your infrastructure is ready to deploy autonomous multi-agent production systems.\", color: \"#00FF9D\" };\n    if (score >= 55) return { name: \"Strategic Scale Phase\", desc: \"You possess robust data foundations, but lack integrated real-time governance and telemetry loop systems.\", color: \"#E98828\" };\n    return { name: \"Discovery & Foundation\", desc: \"Siloed data pipelines and manual compliance. GFF Labs sandbox is recommended to validate high-value cases.\", color: \"#E4000F\" };\n  };\n  const rdTier = getRdTier(rdScore);\n\n  // Tool 4: ROI Calculator State\n  const [roiSize, setRoiSize] = useState(250);\n  const [roiHours, setRoiHours] = useState(8);\n  const [roiRate, setRoiRate] = useState(65);\n\n  const annualHoursSaved = Math.round(roiSize * roiHours * 52 * 0.85);\n  const annualDollarsSaved = annualHoursSaved * roiRate;\n  const implementCost = Math.round(18000 + annualDollarsSaved * 0.08);\n  const netSavings = Math.max(0, annualDollarsSaved - implementCost);\n  const roiPercent = implementCost > 0 ? Math.round((netSavings / implementCost) * 100) : 0;\n\n  // Tool 5: Marketplace State\n  const [activatedApps, setActivatedApps] = useState<Record<string, \"idle\" | \"installing\" | \"installed\">>({\n    auditor: \"idle\",\n    logistics: \"idle\",\n    synthesis: \"idle\",\n  });\n  const [marketLogs, setMarketLogs] = useState<string[]>([]);\n\n  const handleInstallApp = (appId: string, appName: string) => {\n    if (activatedApps[appId] !== \"idle\") return;\n    setActivatedApps((prev) => ({ ...prev, [appId]: \"installing\" }));\n    setMarketLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[Registry] Initiating deployment handshake for: ${appName}...`]);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setMarketLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[Sandbox] Mounting vector indexing cache and validating compliance tags...`]);\n    }, 600);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setActivatedApps((prev) => ({ ...prev, [appId]: \"installed\" }));\n      setMarketLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[SUCCESS] ${appName} fully activated in local secure tenant sandbox.`]);\n    }, 1500);\n  };\n\n  // Tool 6: Foundry Studio State\n  const [selectedNode, setSelectedNode] = useState<string | null>(\"core\");\n  const [flowTesting, setFlowTesting] = useState(false);\n  const [flowLogs, setFlowLogs] = useState<string[]>([]);\n  const [flowConfig, setFlowConfig] = useState({\n    source: \"postgresql\",\n    reasoning: \"react\",\n    guardrail: \"pii\",\n    channel: \"slack\",\n  });\n\n  const runFlowTest = () => {\n    setFlowTesting(true);\n    setFlowLogs([\"[Studio] Compiling workflow DAG graph...\"]);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setFlowLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[Node A] Ingesting telemetry streams from database: [${flowConfig.source.toUpperCase()}]`]);\n    }, 500);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setFlowLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[Node B] Cognitive supervisor activated. Strategy: [${flowConfig.reasoning === \"react\" ? \"ReAct Loop\" : flowConfig.reasoning === \"cot\" ? \"Chain of Thought\" : \"Plan-and-Execute\"}]`]);\n    }, 1000);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setFlowLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[Node C] Compliance check passed. Active Shield: [${flowConfig.guardrail === \"pii\" ? \"PII Redaction\" : \"Toxicity Guard\"}]`]);\n    }, 1500);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setFlowLogs((prev) => [...prev, `[SUCCESS] Output triggered via [${flowConfig.channel.toUpperCase()}] in 450ms. Token cost: $0.0024.`]);\n      setFlowTesting(false);\n    }, 2000);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <section className=\"w-full bg-[#020202] px-6 lg:px-16 lg:py-24 py-16 overflow-hidden relative\">\n      {/* Visual glowing elements */}\n      <div className=\"absolute top-10 left-10 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#009DFF]/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none\" />\n      <div className=\"absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#E4000F]/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none\" />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto relative z-10\">\n        <SectionHeading\n          title={\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[36px] leading-none font-semibold text-center uppercase text-white tracking-wide\">\n              INTERACTIVE <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">EXPERIENCE</span>\n            </h2>\n          }\n          titleClassName=\"text-center\"\n          dividerWidthClassName=\"w-[280px]\"\n        />\n        <p className=\"mt-4 text-center text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/45 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-16\">\n          Hands-on simulation tools. Preview how GFF AI systems operate in secure, sandbox-ready environments.\n        </p>\n\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n          {/* Left: Tab selectors */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-4 space-y-3 order-1\">\n            <h4 className=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-white/40 font-bold mb-4 px-2\">\n              Select Self-Service Tool Sandbox\n            </h4>\n            \n            {/* Mobile horizontal scroll container, desktop vertical list */}\n            <div className=\"flex lg:flex-col gap-3 overflow-x-auto pb-4 lg:pb-0 scrollbar-none snap-x\">\n              {tools.map((t, idx) => {\n                const isActive = activeTab === idx;\n                return (\n                  <button\n                    key={t.id}\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={() => setActiveTab(idx)}\n                    className={`flex-shrink-0 w-[240px] lg:w-full snap-start text-left rounded-[16px] border p-4 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group ${\n                      isActive\n                        ? \"bg-[#050B18] border-white/15 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.12)]\"\n                        : \"bg-[#010101]/60 border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-[#030303]\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    {/* Color Accent Indicator on Active */}\n                    {isActive && (\n                      <motion.div\n                        layoutId=\"activeTabGlow\"\n                        className=\"absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[4px]\"\n                        style={{ backgroundColor: t.color }}\n                      />\n                    )}\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                      <span\n                        className=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\"\n                        style={{ color: isActive ? t.color : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" }}\n                      >\n                        0{idx + 1} // TOOL\n                      </span>\n                      {isActive && (\n                        <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full animate-ping\" style={{ backgroundColor: t.color }} />\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 className={`mt-2 text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] font-semibold transition-colors ${\n                      isActive ? \"text-white\" : \"text-white/60 group-hover:text-white/80\"\n                    }`}>\n                      {t.name}\n                    </h3>\n                    <p className={`mt-1 text-[12px] leading-normal transition-colors line-clamp-1 ${\n                      isActive ? \"text-white/60\" : \"text-white/40\"\n                    }`}>\n                      {t.tagline}\n                    </p>\n                  </button>\n                );\n              })}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Right: Selected Active Sandbox Panel */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 order-2\">\n            <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n              <motion.div\n                key={activeTab}\n                initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 10 }}\n                animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n                exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -10 }}\n                transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}\n                className=\"w-full min-h-[520px] rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-[#04060b] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\"\n              >\n                {/* Header info of selected tool */}\n                <div>\n                  <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-5\">\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider rounded-md uppercase bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/60\">\n                        {tools[activeTab].name} Simulator\n                      </span>\n                      <h2 className=\"mt-2 text-[20px] sm:text-[24px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">\n                        {activeTab === 0 && \"Autonomous Multi-Agent Chat Studio\"}\n                        {activeTab === 1 && \"Enterprise Infrastructure Blueprint Configurator\"}\n                        {activeTab === 2 && \"Infrastructure AI Readiness Assessor\"}\n                        {activeTab === 3 && \"Financial & Productivity ROI Modeler\"}\n                        {activeTab === 4 && \"Enterprise Secure Plug-In Registry\"}\n                        {activeTab === 5 && \"Visual Drag-And-Drop Orchestration Studio\"}\n                      </h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <Link\n                      href={tools[activeTab].link}\n                      className=\"shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-[10px] text-[13px] font-semibold text-white border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] hover:bg-white/[0.1] hover:border-white/20 transition-all self-start sm:self-center\"\n                    >\n                      Launch Tool →\n                    </Link>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Sandbox Inner Playground */}\n                  <div className=\"mt-6\">\n                    {/* Tool 0: Talk to Agent */}\n                    {activeTab === 0 && (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                        <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 leading-normal mb-4\">\n                          Type commands to the GFF Supervisor or click a high-impact preset agentic scenario below.\n                        </p>\n\n                        {/* Terminal Chat Screen */}\n                        <div className=\"h-[280px] rounded-[14px] border border-white/5 bg-black/50 p-4 overflow-y-auto font-mono text-[13px] leading-relaxed space-y-3 scrollbar-thin\">\n                          {chatMessages.map((msg, i) => (\n                            <div\n                              key={i}\n                              className={`flex ${\n                                msg.sender === \"user\" ? \"justify-end\" : \"justify-start\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <div\n                                className={`max-w-[85%] rounded-[12px] px-3.5 py-2 ${\n                                  msg.isLog\n                                    ? \"text-[#8EA6D8] bg-white/[0.02] border-l-2 border-[#009DFF]/40 pl-3 w-full\"\n                                    : msg.sender === \"user\"\n                                    ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/15 text-white border border-[#009DFF]/30\"\n                                    : \"bg-white/[0.04] text-white/90 border border-white/5\"\n                                }`}\n                              >\n                                {msg.sender === \"user\" ? (\n                                  <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] mr-1.5\">&gt;</span>\n                                ) : !msg.isLog ? (\n                                  <span className=\"text-[#FF4A5A] mr-1.5\">[GFF Supervisor]</span>\n                                ) : null}\n                                <span>{msg.text}</span>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                          ))}\n                          {chatLoading && (\n                            <div className=\"flex justify-start\">\n                              <div className=\"bg-white/[0.03] text-white/50 rounded-[12px] px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2\">\n                                <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-bounce\" />\n                                <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-bounce [animation-delay:0.2s]\" />\n                                <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-bounce [animation-delay:0.4s]\" />\n                                <span className=\"text-xs text-white/40\">Supervisor composing graph...</span>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                          )}\n                          <div ref={chatBottomRef} />\n                        </div>\n\n                        {/* Presets and custom text */}\n                        <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2\">\n                          <button\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => handleSendChat(\"Optimize Cloud Spend\")}\n                            disabled={chatLoading}\n                            className=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 text-xs text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors\"\n                          >\n                            ⚡ Cloud Optimization\n                          </button>\n                          <button\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => handleSendChat(\"Audit Compliance & Security\")}\n                            disabled={chatLoading}\n                            className=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 text-xs text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors\"\n                          >\n                            🛡️ Compliance Scan\n                          </button>\n                          <button\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => handleSendChat(\"Verify Supply Chain Route\")}\n                            disabled={chatLoading}\n                            className=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 text-xs text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors\"\n                          >\n                            🌐 Logistics Router\n                          </button>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <form\n                          onSubmit={(e) => {\n                            e.preventDefault();\n                            handleSendChat(chatInput);\n                          }}\n                          className=\"flex gap-2 pt-2\"\n                        >\n                          <input\n                            type=\"text\"\n                            value={chatInput}\n                            onChange={(e) => setChatInput(e.target.value)}\n                            placeholder=\"Type a custom command (e.g. Audit legacy SQL triggers)...\"\n                            className=\"flex-grow h-[42px] rounded-[10px] border border-white/10 bg-[#010101]/60 px-4 text-[13px] text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/50\"\n                          />\n                          <button\n                            type=\"submit\"\n                            disabled={chatLoading || !chatInput.trim()}\n                            className=\"px-5 h-[42px] rounded-[10px] text-white text-[13px] font-semibold transition-all\"\n                            style={{ background: \"linear-gradient(270deg, #009DFF 0%, #4835C6 100%)\" }}\n                          >\n                            Send\n                          </button>\n                        </form>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* Tool 1: Blueprint Generator */}\n                    {activeTab === 1 && (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                        <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 leading-normal\">\n                          Customize enterprise operational variables to generate a sandbox visual schema of GFF agent roles.\n                        </p>\n\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                          <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                            <label className=\"text-[12px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Scale Target</label>\n                            <select\n                              value={bpObjective}\n                              onChange={(e) => {\n                                setBpObjective(e.target.value);\n                                setBpGenerated(false);\n                              }}\n                              className=\"w-full h-[40px] rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] px-3 text-xs text-white/80 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#E98828]\"\n                            >\n                              <option value=\"optimize\">Department Productivity</option>\n                              <option value=\"orchestrate\">Multi-Agent Ecosystem</option>\n                              <option value=\"global\">Global Enterprise Fleet</option>\n                            </select>\n                          </div>\n\n                          <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                            <label className=\"text-[12px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Integrations</label>\n                            <select\n                              value={bpInt}\n                              onChange={(e) => {\n                                setBpInt(e.target.value);\n                                setBpGenerated(false);\n                              }}\n                              className=\"w-full h-[40px] rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] px-3 text-xs text-white/80 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#E98828]\"\n                            >\n                              <option value=\"api\">SaaS API Connectors</option>\n                              <option value=\"events\">Event-Driven Pipes</option>\n                              <option value=\"database\">Native Direct SQL Cache</option>\n                            </select>\n                          </div>\n\n                          <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                            <label className=\"text-[12px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Security Layer</label>\n                            <select\n                              value={bpSec}\n                              onChange={(e) => {\n                                setBpSec(e.target.value);\n                                setBpGenerated(false);\n                              }}\n                              className=\"w-full h-[40px] rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] px-3 text-xs text-white/80 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#E98828]\"\n                            >\n                              <option value=\"cloud\">Cloud-Hosted Shared Tenant</option>\n                              <option value=\"vpc\">Private VPC Single-Tenant</option>\n                              <option value=\"sovereign\">Sovereign Air-Gapped Cluster</option>\n                            </select>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"flex justify-center pt-2\">\n                          <button\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={handleGenerateBp}\n                            disabled={bpGenerating}\n                            className=\"px-6 h-[44px] rounded-[10px] text-white text-[14px] font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all\"\n                            style={{ background: \"linear-gradient(270deg, #E98828 0%, #B11C58 100%)\" }}\n                          >\n                            {bpGenerating ? \"Mapping Pipelines...\" : \"Generate Blueprint Preview\"}\n                          </button>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n                          {bpGenerated && (\n                            <motion.div\n                              initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.98 }}\n                              animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}\n                              exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.98 }}\n                              className=\"rounded-[14px] border border-white/10 bg-[#070c18] p-5 space-y-4\"\n                            >\n                              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                                <span className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-[#E98828] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                                  Structural Schema Generated\n                                </span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/45\">\n                                  DAG-UUID: {Math.random().toString(36).substr(2, 9).toUpperCase()}\n                                </span>\n                              </div>\n                              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-xs\">\n                                <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                                  <p className=\"text-white/40\">DEPLOYMENT LANDSCAPE</p>\n                                  <p className=\"font-semibold text-white\">\n                                    {bpSec === \"cloud\" && \"Standard Cloud Container (SaaS/Shared)\"}\n                                    {bpSec === \"vpc\" && \"Hardened Private VPC Secure Orchestrator\"}\n                                    {bpSec === \"sovereign\" && \"Air-Gapped Sovereign Cluster Engine\"}\n                                  </p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                                  <p className=\"text-white/40\">INTEGRATION STRATEGY</p>\n                                  <p className=\"font-semibold text-white\">\n                                    {bpInt === \"api\" && \"Synchronous REST Endpoint Mapping\"}\n                                    {bpInt === \"events\" && \"Asynchronous Event-Driven Stream Hooks\"}\n                                    {bpInt === \"database\" && \"Direct Real-time DB Index Memory Access\"}\n                                  </p>\n                                </div>\n                              </div>\n                              <div className=\"p-3 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-[8px] border border-white/5 text-xs text-white/60 leading-normal\">\n                                <span className=\"text-[#E98828] font-bold\">Recommendation:</span> Based on your selection, we advise a multi-agent cluster orchestrated with active token observability to prevent latency leakage.\n                              </div>\n\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-end\">\n                                <button\n                                  type=\"button\"\n                                  onClick={scrollSmoothToBlueprintSection}\n                                  className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-[#E98828] hover:underline\"\n                                >\n                                  Scroll to Full Blueprint Generator below &darr;\n                                </button>\n                              </div>\n                            </motion.div>\n                          )}\n                        </AnimatePresence>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* Tool 2: AI Readiness */}\n                    {activeTab === 2 && (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                        <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 leading-normal\">\n                          Adjust the evaluation levers below to see your computed Readiness score and recommendations.\n                        </p>\n\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-center\">\n                          {/* Sliders */}\n                          <div className=\"md:col-span-8 space-y-5\">\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs\">\n                                <span className=\"font-semibold text-white/80\">Data Organization</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[#9D00FF] font-bold\">LVL {rdData} / 5</span>\n                              </div>\n                              <input\n                                type=\"range\"\n                                min=\"1\"\n                                max=\"5\"\n                                value={rdData}\n                                onChange={(e) => setRdData(Number(e.target.value))}\n                                className=\"w-full accent-[#9D00FF]\"\n                              />\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] text-white/30\">\n                                <span>Siloed RDBMS</span>\n                                <span>Unified Vector Graph</span>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs\">\n                                <span className=\"font-semibold text-white/80\">Governance & Compliances</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[#9D00FF] font-bold\">LVL {rdCompliance} / 5</span>\n                              </div>\n                              <input\n                                type=\"range\"\n                                min=\"1\"\n                                max=\"5\"\n                                value={rdCompliance}\n                                onChange={(e) => setRdCompliance(Number(e.target.value))}\n                                className=\"w-full accent-[#9D00FF]\"\n                              />\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] text-white/30\">\n                                <span>Ad-Hoc Manual Audit</span>\n                                <span>SOC2 Realtime Guardrails</span>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs\">\n                                <span className=\"font-semibold text-white/80\">Agent Deployments</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[#9D00FF] font-bold\">LVL {rdAgent} / 5</span>\n                              </div>\n                              <input\n                                type=\"range\"\n                                min=\"1\"\n                                max=\"5\"\n                                value={rdAgent}\n                                onChange={(e) => setRdAgent(Number(e.target.value))}\n                                className=\"w-full accent-[#9D00FF]\"\n                              />\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] text-white/30\">\n                                <span>Simple Chatbots</span>\n                                <span>Autonomous Orchestrators</span>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n\n                          {/* Gauge/Visual Result */}\n                          <div className=\"md:col-span-4 flex flex-col items-center p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-[#010101]/40\">\n                            <div className=\"relative w-28 h-28 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                              {/* Radial progress ring */}\n                              <svg className=\"w-full h-full transform -rotate-90\">\n                                <circle\n                                  cx=\"56\"\n                                  cy=\"56\"\n                                  r=\"48\"\n                                  stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\"\n                                  strokeWidth=\"6\"\n                                  fill=\"transparent\"\n                                />\n                                <circle\n                                  cx=\"56\"\n                                  cy=\"56\"\n                                  r=\"48\"\n                                  stroke={rdTier.color}\n                                  strokeWidth=\"6\"\n                                  fill=\"transparent\"\n                                  strokeDasharray={2 * Math.PI * 48}\n                                  strokeDashoffset={\n                                    2 * Math.PI * 48 * (1 - rdScore / 100)\n                                  }\n                                  className=\"transition-all duration-300\"\n                                />\n                              </svg>\n                              <div className=\"absolute flex flex-col items-center\">\n                                <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">{rdScore}%</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40\">Readiness</span>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <span className=\"mt-4 text-[13px] font-bold text-center\" style={{ color: rdTier.color }}>\n                              {rdTier.name}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"rounded-[12px] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n                          <p className=\"font-semibold text-white mb-1\">Tailored Action Recommendation:</p>\n                          {rdTier.desc}\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* Tool 3: ROI Calculator */}\n                    {activeTab === 3 && (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                        <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 leading-normal\">\n                          Model projected annual savings based on workforce size and weekly process hours saved.\n                        </p>\n\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                          {/* Inputs */}\n                          <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs\">\n                                <span className=\"font-semibold text-white/80\">Workgroup Size</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{roiSize} employees</span>\n                              </div>\n                              <input\n                                type=\"range\"\n                                min=\"10\"\n                                max=\"2000\"\n                                step=\"10\"\n                                value={roiSize}\n                                onChange={(e) => setRoiSize(Number(e.target.value))}\n                                className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\"\n                              />\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs\">\n                                <span className=\"font-semibold text-white/80\">Weekly Hours Automated / Employee</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{roiHours} hours</span>\n                              </div>\n                              <input\n                                type=\"range\"\n                                min=\"2\"\n                                max=\"24\"\n                                step=\"1\"\n                                value={roiHours}\n                                onChange={(e) => setRoiHours(Number(e.target.value))}\n                                className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\"\n                              />\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs\">\n                                <span className=\"font-semibold text-white/80\">Average Hourly Rate</span>\n                                <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">${roiRate} / hour</span>\n                              </div>\n                              <input\n                                type=\"range\"\n                                min=\"20\"\n                                max=\"180\"\n                                step=\"5\"\n                                value={roiRate}\n                                onChange={(e) => setRoiRate(Number(e.target.value))}\n                                className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\"\n                              />\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n\n                          {/* Outputs */}\n                          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                            <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40\">Hours Saved/Yr</span>\n                              <span className=\"mt-1 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white\">\n                                {annualHoursSaved.toLocaleString()}\n                              </span>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40\">Value Created</span>\n                              <span className=\"mt-1 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#00FF9D]\">\n                                ${annualDollarsSaved.toLocaleString()}\n                              </span>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40\">Est. GFF License</span>\n                              <span className=\"mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white/70\">\n                                ${implementCost.toLocaleString()}\n                              </span>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40\">Projected Net ROI</span>\n                              <span className=\"mt-1 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">\n                                {roiPercent}%\n                              </span>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"rounded-[12px] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-xs text-white/50 text-center\">\n                          Formula applies standard 85% orchestration execution efficiency over 52 working weeks.\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* Tool 4: Marketplace */}\n                    {activeTab === 4 && (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                        <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 leading-normal\">\n                          Deploy high-impact autonomous pipelines directly into your tenant mock container.\n                        </p>\n\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                          {/* App 1 */}\n                          <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] flex flex-col justify-between\">\n                            <div>\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#0186E4] uppercase font-bold\">Compliance Node</span>\n                              <h4 className=\"mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-white\">Sovereign Compliance Guard</h4>\n                              <p className=\"mt-2 text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n                                Audits public S3 buckets & IAM profiles continuously to prevent credential exposure.\n                              </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => handleInstallApp(\"auditor\", \"Sovereign Compliance Guard\")}\n                              className={`mt-4 w-full h-[34px] rounded-[6px] text-xs font-semibold transition-all ${\n                                activatedApps.auditor === \"installed\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border border-[#00FF9D]/30 text-[#00FF9D]\"\n                                  : activatedApps.auditor === \"installing\"\n                                  ? \"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/40 cursor-not-allowed\"\n                                  : \"bg-[#0186E4] hover:bg-[#0186E4]/80 text-white\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              {activatedApps.auditor === \"installed\" && \"✓ Live in Sandbox\"}\n                              {activatedApps.auditor === \"installing\" && \"Mounting...\"}\n                              {activatedApps.auditor === \"idle\" && \"Deploy Sandbox\"}\n                            </button>\n                          </div>\n\n                          {/* App 2 */}\n                          <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] flex flex-col justify-between\">\n                            <div>\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#0186E4] uppercase font-bold\">Logistics Hook</span>\n                              <h4 className=\"mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-white\">Supply Chain Resilient Route</h4>\n                              <p className=\"mt-2 text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n                                Intercepts marine cargo tracking pipelines to automatically re-route inland shipping corridors.\n                              </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => handleInstallApp(\"logistics\", \"Supply Chain Resilient Route\")}\n                              className={`mt-4 w-full h-[34px] rounded-[6px] text-xs font-semibold transition-all ${\n                                activatedApps.logistics === \"installed\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border border-[#00FF9D]/30 text-[#00FF9D]\"\n                                  : activatedApps.logistics === \"installing\"\n                                  ? \"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/40 cursor-not-allowed\"\n                                  : \"bg-[#0186E4] hover:bg-[#0186E4]/80 text-white\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              {activatedApps.logistics === \"installed\" && \"✓ Live in Sandbox\"}\n                              {activatedApps.logistics === \"installing\" && \"Mounting...\"}\n                              {activatedApps.logistics === \"idle\" && \"Deploy Sandbox\"}\n                            </button>\n                          </div>\n\n                          {/* App 3 */}\n                          <div className=\"p-4 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] flex flex-col justify-between\">\n                            <div>\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#0186E4] uppercase font-bold\">Strategy Agent</span>\n                              <h4 className=\"mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-white\">Quarterly Executive Digest</h4>\n                              <p className=\"mt-2 text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n                                Compiles multiple departmental raw CSV files into consolidated presentation decks.\n                              </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => handleInstallApp(\"synthesis\", \"Quarterly Executive Digest\")}\n                              className={`mt-4 w-full h-[34px] rounded-[6px] text-xs font-semibold transition-all ${\n                                activatedApps.synthesis === \"installed\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border border-[#00FF9D]/30 text-[#00FF9D]\"\n                                  : activatedApps.synthesis === \"installing\"\n                                  ? \"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/40 cursor-not-allowed\"\n                                  : \"bg-[#0186E4] hover:bg-[#0186E4]/80 text-white\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              {activatedApps.synthesis === \"installed\" && \"✓ Live in Sandbox\"}\n                              {activatedApps.synthesis === \"installing\" && \"Mounting...\"}\n                              {activatedApps.synthesis === \"idle\" && \"Deploy Sandbox\"}\n                            </button>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        {/* Marketplace Logs */}\n                        <div className=\"h-[100px] rounded-[10px] border border-white/5 bg-black/40 p-3 overflow-y-auto font-mono text-[11px] text-white/60 space-y-1\">\n                          {marketLogs.length === 0 ? (\n                            <span className=\"text-white/30 italic\">No apps active yet. Click &quot;Deploy Sandbox&quot; to test.</span>\n                          ) : (\n                            marketLogs.map((log, idx) => <p key={idx}>{log}</p>)\n                          )}\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* Tool 5: Foundry Studio */}\n                    {activeTab === 5 && (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                        <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 leading-normal\">\n                          Interact with GFF’s visual multi-agent workflow DAG. Click nodes to configure cognitive logic.\n                        </p>\n\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6\">\n                          {/* Visual Flow Canvas */}\n                          <div className=\"md:col-span-7 h-[240px] rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-black/60 relative flex items-center justify-around overflow-hidden p-4\">\n                            {/* SVG Connection Lines */}\n                            <svg className=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none\">\n                              <path\n                                d=\"M 60 120 Q 150 60 210 120\"\n                                fill=\"none\"\n                                stroke={selectedNode === \"source\" ? \"#00FF9D\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"}\n                                strokeWidth=\"2\"\n                                strokeDasharray=\"4 4\"\n                                className=\"animate-[dash_20s_linear_infinite]\"\n                              />\n                              <path\n                                d=\"M 210 120 Q 280 180 340 120\"\n                                fill=\"none\"\n                                stroke={selectedNode === \"core\" ? \"#00FF9D\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"}\n                                strokeWidth=\"2\"\n                                strokeDasharray=\"4 4\"\n                                className=\"animate-[dash_20s_linear_infinite]\"\n                              />\n                              <path\n                                d=\"M 340 120 Q 400 60 480 120\"\n                                fill=\"none\"\n                                stroke={selectedNode === \"guard\" ? \"#00FF9D\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"}\n                                strokeWidth=\"2\"\n                                strokeDasharray=\"4 4\"\n                                className=\"animate-[dash_20s_linear_infinite]\"\n                              />\n                            </svg>\n\n                            {/* Node 1 */}\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setSelectedNode(\"source\")}\n                              className={`z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-[12px] border flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-all ${\n                                selectedNode === \"source\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border-[#00FF9D] text-white shadow-lg shadow-[#00FF9D]/5\"\n                                  : \"bg-white/[0.03] border-white/10 text-white/60 hover:border-white/20\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-[18px]\">📥</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold mt-1 uppercase\">Source</span>\n                            </button>\n\n                            {/* Node 2 */}\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setSelectedNode(\"core\")}\n                              className={`z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-[12px] border flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-all ${\n                                selectedNode === \"core\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border-[#00FF9D] text-white shadow-lg shadow-[#00FF9D]/5\"\n                                  : \"bg-white/[0.03] border-white/10 text-white/60 hover:border-white/20\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-[18px]\">🧠</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold mt-1 uppercase\">Core</span>\n                            </button>\n\n                            {/* Node 3 */}\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setSelectedNode(\"guard\")}\n                              className={`z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-[12px] border flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-all ${\n                                selectedNode === \"guard\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border-[#00FF9D] text-white shadow-lg shadow-[#00FF9D]/5\"\n                                  : \"bg-white/[0.03] border-white/10 text-white/60 hover:border-white/20\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-[18px]\">🛡️</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold mt-1 uppercase\">Shield</span>\n                            </button>\n\n                            {/* Node 4 */}\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setSelectedNode(\"action\")}\n                              className={`z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-[12px] border flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-all ${\n                                selectedNode === \"action\"\n                                  ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border-[#00FF9D] text-white shadow-lg shadow-[#00FF9D]/5\"\n                                  : \"bg-white/[0.03] border-white/10 text-white/60 hover:border-white/20\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-[18px]\">📤</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold mt-1 uppercase\">Output</span>\n                            </button>\n                          </div>\n\n                          {/* Configuration / Side Controls */}\n                          <div className=\"md:col-span-5 rounded-[16px] border border-white/5 bg-[#010101]/40 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n                            <div>\n                              <h4 className=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold text-[#00FF9D]\">\n                                {selectedNode === \"source\" && \"Node: Data Source Ingestion\"}\n                                {selectedNode === \"core\" && \"Node: Reasoning Supervisor\"}\n                                {selectedNode === \"guard\" && \"Node: Compliance Shield\"}\n                                {selectedNode === \"action\" && \"Node: Workflow Output Channel\"}\n                              </h4>\n\n                              {/* Custom Config Parameters based on Selected Node */}\n                              <div className=\"mt-4 space-y-3\">\n                                {selectedNode === \"source\" && (\n                                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                                    <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Ingestion Store</label>\n                                    <select\n                                      value={flowConfig.source}\n                                      onChange={(e) => setFlowConfig((prev) => ({ ...prev, source: e.target.value }))}\n                                      className=\"w-full h-[32px] rounded-[6px] border border-white/10 bg-transparent px-2 text-xs text-white\"\n                                    >\n                                      <option value=\"postgresql\">PostgreSQL Database</option>\n                                      <option value=\"snowflake\">Snowflake Cluster</option>\n                                      <option value=\"s3\">AWS S3 Vector Cache</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                  </div>\n                                )}\n\n                                {selectedNode === \"core\" && (\n                                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                                    <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Cognitive Process</label>\n                                    <select\n                                      value={flowConfig.reasoning}\n                                      onChange={(e) => setFlowConfig((prev) => ({ ...prev, reasoning: e.target.value }))}\n                                      className=\"w-full h-[32px] rounded-[6px] border border-white/10 bg-transparent px-2 text-xs text-white\"\n                                    >\n                                      <option value=\"react\">ReAct Feedback Loop</option>\n                                      <option value=\"cot\">Chain-of-Thought</option>\n                                      <option value=\"p-e\">Plan-and-Execute</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                  </div>\n                                )}\n\n                                {selectedNode === \"guard\" && (\n                                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                                    <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Guardrail Policy</label>\n                                    <select\n                                      value={flowConfig.guardrail}\n                                      onChange={(e) => setFlowConfig((prev) => ({ ...prev, guardrail: e.target.value }))}\n                                      className=\"w-full h-[32px] rounded-[6px] border border-white/10 bg-transparent px-2 text-xs text-white\"\n                                    >\n                                      <option value=\"pii\">PII & GDPR Redaction</option>\n                                      <option value=\"tox\">Toxicity Shield Filter</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                  </div>\n                                )}\n\n                                {selectedNode === \"action\" && (\n                                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                                    <label className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Output Trigger</label>\n                                    <select\n                                      value={flowConfig.channel}\n                                      onChange={(e) => setFlowConfig((prev) => ({ ...prev, channel: e.target.value }))}\n                                      className=\"w-full h-[32px] rounded-[6px] border border-white/10 bg-transparent px-2 text-xs text-white\"\n                                    >\n                                      <option value=\"slack\">Slack Operational Alert</option>\n                                      <option value=\"webhook\">Automated REST Webhook</option>\n                                      <option value=\"erp\">SAP System Update</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                  </div>\n                                )}\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={runFlowTest}\n                              disabled={flowTesting}\n                              className=\"mt-6 w-full h-[38px] rounded-[8px] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 text-xs text-white font-semibold transition-all\"\n                            >\n                              {flowTesting ? \"Executing workflow...\" : \"Execute Flow Test\"}\n                            </button>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        {/* Execution Console */}\n                        <div className=\"h-[90px] rounded-[10px] border border-white/5 bg-black/40 p-3 overflow-y-auto font-mono text-[11px] text-white/60 space-y-1\">\n                          {flowLogs.length === 0 ? (\n                            <span className=\"text-white/30 italic\">Click &quot;Execute Flow Test&quot; to test DAG pipeline sequence.</span>\n                          ) : (\n                            flowLogs.map((log, idx) => <p key={idx}>{log}</p>)\n                          )}\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Footer linking actions */}\n                <div className=\"mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 text-xs\">\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40\">\n                    * Sandbox previews operate using simulated local vectors. Secure live cluster credentials required for real execution.\n                  </span>\n                  <Link\n                    href={tools[activeTab].link}\n                    className=\"shrink-0 text-[#009DFF] font-bold hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1\"\n                  >\n                    Launch Full stand-alone Sandbox Tool &rarr;\n                  </Link>\n                </div>\n              </motion.div>\n            </AnimatePresence>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  );\n}"}}}
