ing system, presented in a tabular/card report. For the `/build/roi` route, I'm constructing a financial model to quantify cost reductions and productivity gains. I also have an SVG diagram block or schema view in mind.\n\n\n**Expanding the ROI Model**\n\nI'm expanding the ROI calculator further, and I'm adding detailed sliders for Employee Turnover, License Costs, and SLA compliance. I'm also implementing glowing financial cards for a visually appealing presentation. The aim is to create a robust and compelling tool that quantifies cost reductions and productivity gains clearly, for claims across multi-agent enterprise fleets.\n\n\n"}}
